'''''Monophyllanthe''''' is a genus of plants native to [[Brazil]], [[Colombia]], [[French Guinea]] and [[Suriname]].<ref>[http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/namedetail.do?name_id=254590 Kew World Checklist of Selected Plant Families, ''Monophyllanthe'']</ref><ref>K.Schum. in H.G.A.Engler (ed.). 1902. Das Pflanzenreich IV. 48 (Heft 11): 165.</ref> It contains 2 recognized species:
*''[[Monophyllanthe araracuarensis]]'' <small>S.Su√°rez, Galeano & H.Kenn.</small> - Brazil and Colombia
*''[[Monophyllanthe oligophylla]]'' <small>K.Schum.</small> - French Guiana and Suriname

